cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper deals with object detection and segmentation in video streams, which is a topic closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a specialized memory cell and a Q-learning-based policy training strategy, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the potential applications of their approach in robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
